OL,3,CMan charged with murder of woman in
OL,4,CWakefield
OL,6,FA man from Wakefield has been charged
OL,7,Fwith the murder of a woman who was
OL,8,Ffound dead at a property in Horbury.
OL,10,FDavid Barraclough, aged 45, of Ken
OL,11,FChurchill Drive, has been charged with
OL,12,Fthe murder of Carolann Barraclough,
OL,13,Faged 37.
OL,15,FBarraclough has been remanded into
OL,16,Fcustody and is due to appear at Leeds
OL,17,FMagistrates Court on Monday 9 March.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
