OL,3,CMan charged with murder of woman in
OL,4,CWakefield
OL,6,FPolice attended at a property Ken
OL,7,FChurchill Drive on Thursday 5 March
OL,8,Fafter officers received a concern for
OL,9,Fsafety report for a woman at an
OL,10,Faddress there.
OL,12,FFollowing searches, Carolann's body
OL,13,Fwas located at the property.
